transcripts.text: Trump came the carrier and told him he was saving all the jobs.  And that was bull.  I was in the third row.  People cheered, people clapped, people cried.  They wanted something to believe in.  I had to tell the people their jobs were going to Mexico.  They were devastated.  People lost their health care and their retirement.  All Trump cares about is cutting taxes for the people at the top.  The same companies that are shipping our jobs out of this country.  Working people got to fight back.
